feat: STM SQLite ring buffer with FIFO eviction and semantic dedup (hr-31j.1)

Implements internal/memory/stm.go — a SQLite-backed short-term memory ring
buffer with 100-item capacity, 7-day TTL, cosine-similarity dedup on insert,
and auto-promotion of high-importance items to LTM on eviction via the
LTMPromoter interface. Includes 14 tests covering all behaviors.

